1
00:00:01,620 --> 00:00:03,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're here again? What a pest.</font>

2
00:00:03,970 --> 00:00:06,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Selio-san.</font>

3
00:00:06,320 --> 00:00:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look as busy as ever.</font>

4
00:00:08,290 --> 00:00:10,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I'm busy.</font>

5
00:00:10,290 --> 00:00:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't get any work done because of you.</font>

6
00:00:13,150 --> 00:00:15,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wouldn't mind if you let me be.</i></font>

7
00:00:17,350 --> 00:00:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Looks like he's finally planning 
on monitoring me all day.</i></font>

8
00:00:20,910 --> 00:00:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Selio!</font>

9
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:26,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing? Why aren't 
you helping in the almshouse?</font>

10
00:00:26,380 --> 00:00:29,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Well, I was assigned
 to watch over this guy today,</font>

11
00:00:29,770 --> 00:00:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you'll need someone else to...</font>

12
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just leave that guy alone.</font>

13
00:00:33,420 --> 00:00:36,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's merely the tagalong from
 another world who can't do anything.</font>

14
00:00:36,740 --> 00:00:39,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't dump your work
 in the almshouse on me!</font>

15
00:00:41,760 --> 00:00:43,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay...</font>

16
00:00:43,270 --> 00:00:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do anything inappropriate, 
otherworld commoner.</font>

17
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:52,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's how you ended up here?</font>

18
00:00:52,610 --> 00:00:53,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

19
00:00:53,400 --> 00:00:56,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gracious, what troublesome children.</font>

20
00:00:56,430 --> 00:00:59,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will fetch Selio, so kindly 
return to the other room.</font>

21
00:00:59,840 --> 00:01:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, in that case, let me 
accompany you to the almshouse.</font>

22
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:06,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

23
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:10,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since the almshouse is part of the church,
it's also under investigation.</font>

24
00:01:10,630 --> 00:01:12,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, if I go there instead,</font>

25
00:01:12,340 --> 00:01:16,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Selio-san can continue watching me 
while doing his part in the almshouse.</font>

26
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wouldn't that be more efficient?</font>

27
00:01:33,780 --> 00:01:38,910
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}ISEKAI OFFICE WORKER: THE OTHER WORLD'S
BOOKS DEPEND ON THE BEAN COUNTER</font>

28
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:56,190
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}EPISODE 9: I MADE A PLAN</font>

29
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So this is the almshouse...</i></font>

30
00:02:55,740 --> 00:02:59,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're currently caring for 
28 children here, correct?</font>

31
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:02,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did you get that information?</font>

32
00:03:02,020 --> 00:03:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was in those documents.</font>

33
00:03:04,100 --> 00:03:08,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does your shamelessness come
 from being a civil servant? Or...</font>

34
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's probably due to my personality.</font>

35
00:03:10,950 --> 00:03:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do the children have to graduate
the almshouse at a certain age?</font>

36
00:03:14,780 --> 00:03:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed.</font>

37
00:03:16,220 --> 00:03:19,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The almshouse only cares for 
them until the age of twelve.</font>

38
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:23,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After that, they must either 
train as monks or take civilian jobs.</font>

39
00:03:24,020 --> 00:03:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. What kind of work do they...</font>

40
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:29,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Disciple, with all due respect,</font>

41
00:03:29,490 --> 00:03:32,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you should act in a manner a little 
more befitting a disciple of Abran.</font>

42
00:03:32,980 --> 00:03:34,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not a disciple.</font>

43
00:03:34,870 --> 00:03:38,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, where do the children 
without families end up working?</font>

44
00:03:39,310 --> 00:03:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most of them apprentice with craftsmen.</font>

45
00:03:41,890 --> 00:03:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Craftsmen?</font>

46
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:47,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They don't take jobs that make 
use of their magical energy?</font>

47
00:03:48,140 --> 00:03:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know what you've 
heard from where, but...</font>

48
00:03:51,730 --> 00:03:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are many children here</font>

49
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:57,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who cannot control their magical energy 
and had to leave their families.</font>

50
00:03:57,680 --> 00:04:02,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We teach them how to control their power 
so that they may lead normal lives.</font>

51
00:04:02,790 --> 00:04:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're in the church's care to keep 
their magical energy in check...</i></font>

52
00:04:06,350 --> 00:04:08,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aresh-sama said the same thing.</i></font>

53
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:12,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Either way, I can feel his magical 
energy waves through my barrier.</i></font>

54
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:16,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It would be unwise to press him further.</i></font>

55
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You!</font>

56
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you come here for?!</font>

57
00:04:23,580 --> 00:04:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought it would be easier 
for you to watch me this way</font>

58
00:04:27,250 --> 00:04:29,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">while you're working in the almshouse.</font>

59
00:04:29,890 --> 00:04:33,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Selio, Fredrik should have been the one 
responsible for the almshouse today.</font>

60
00:04:33,620 --> 00:04:35,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That's...</font>

61
00:04:35,080 --> 00:04:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good grief. Come to me if something 
like this happens again.</font>

62
00:04:39,620 --> 00:04:40,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's likely impossible.</i></font>

63
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd wager this is a common occurrence, 
and snitching would only make it worse.</i></font>

64
00:04:47,530 --> 00:04:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no need for a civil servant 
like you to come to the almshouse!</font>

65
00:04:50,650 --> 00:04:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Oh! Kondou-san, you're here!</font>

66
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:56,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you really are visiting the church!</font>

67
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What brings you here today?</font>

68
00:04:58,510 --> 00:04:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm on my inspection.</font>

69
00:04:59,790 --> 00:05:02,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here, Shiraishi-san?</font>

70
00:05:02,280 --> 00:05:06,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lately, I've been helping out 
here in the almshouse.</font>

71
00:05:06,190 --> 00:05:07,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so?</font>

72
00:05:07,530 --> 00:05:08,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

73
00:05:09,340 --> 00:05:11,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The holy maiden is doing other work?</i></font>

74
00:05:11,780 --> 00:05:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even though she's the only one
with purification magic?</i></font>

75
00:05:14,610 --> 00:05:18,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I happened to meet an orphaned child 
who came to the chapel and...</font>

76
00:05:19,150 --> 00:05:22,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but this church...</font>

77
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:26,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um, I thought the two 
of you didn't get along.</font>

78
00:05:26,260 --> 00:05:27,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

79
00:05:27,870 --> 00:05:31,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, this guy is trying to destroy 
the holy maiden's prestige.</font>

80
00:05:31,940 --> 00:05:36,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could he be talking about the plan 
to eliminate the holy maiden system?</i></font>

81
00:05:36,300 --> 00:05:40,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would that make Kondou-san 
and I dislike each other?</font>

82
00:05:40,450 --> 00:05:44,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why? Because the importance 
of the holy maiden will...</font>

83
00:05:44,390 --> 00:05:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see.</i></font>

84
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:50,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This must be the reason everyone
 at the church has been so unfriendly.</i></font>

85
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right!</font>

86
00:05:52,250 --> 00:05:55,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once the holy maiden system's abolished,
I'll be able to go back to my world.</font>

87
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:57,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't be happier!</font>

88
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:00,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

89
00:06:01,310 --> 00:06:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The children here in the almshouse
 don't receive any sort of education.</font>

90
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come again?</font>

91
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They aren't allowed to go to school,</font>

92
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and they spend each day here working</font>

93
00:06:12,170 --> 00:06:14,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and doing all the housekeeping
for the communal areas.</font>

94
00:06:15,590 --> 00:06:20,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really don't think it's a very good
situation for these children's futures.</font>

95
00:06:20,350 --> 00:06:22,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Shiraishi-san...</font>

96
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:27,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand that not 
everyone can attend school.</font>

97
00:06:27,510 --> 00:06:30,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's such a shame that 
they lose the opportunity</font>

98
00:06:30,030 --> 00:06:32,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to learn just because 
they don't have parents.</font>

99
00:06:33,180 --> 00:06:35,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is a different world.</i></font>

100
00:06:35,060 --> 00:06:37,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We shouldn't compare it to modern Japan.</i></font>

101
00:06:37,880 --> 00:06:39,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Still...</i></font>

102
00:06:39,540 --> 00:06:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Losing precious talent and human resources</i></font>

103
00:06:41,660 --> 00:06:44,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>over their birth or upbringing
is a huge loss for any country.</i></font>

104
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:48,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sigma, who made my abacus, 
is undoubtedly talented.</i></font>

105
00:06:48,790 --> 00:06:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not utilizing the kids' magical
energy also seems a waste.</i></font>

106
00:06:51,770 --> 00:06:54,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Above all, they have no freedom 
to choose their occupations.</i></font>

107
00:06:55,820 --> 00:06:59,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I was wondering if 
we could do something...</font>

108
00:06:59,850 --> 00:07:02,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so kind, Your Holiness.</font>

109
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:05,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's impossible.</font>

110
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:10,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The almshouse doesn't have 
the time or money for that.</font>

111
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But even you, Selio-kun...</font>

112
00:07:13,940 --> 00:07:17,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you have a dream job 
when you were a child?</font>

113
00:07:17,820 --> 00:07:19,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

114
00:07:21,140 --> 00:07:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The little children here 
often tell me their dreams.</font>

115
00:07:24,170 --> 00:07:27,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"When I grow up, I want to become 
a sorcerer working in the castle."</font>

116
00:07:27,650 --> 00:07:29,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I want to become a knight."</font>

117
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:33,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's wrong that they end up unable
to honestly say such things anymore</font>

118
00:07:33,970 --> 00:07:35,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and abandon all hope.</font>

119
00:07:36,380 --> 00:07:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must have come from a very 
peaceful world, Your Holiness.</font>

120
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The world I'm from sees war 
and discrimination, too.</font>

121
00:07:48,010 --> 00:07:49,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We even have almshouses.</font>

122
00:07:50,130 --> 00:07:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we still have the freedom 
to achieve our dreams.</font>

123
00:07:55,970 --> 00:07:58,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's impossible...</font>

124
00:07:59,740 --> 00:08:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not possible to change everything 
at once, no, but it's worth consideration.</font>

125
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's difficult to expand an education 
initiative in one fell swoop,</font>

126
00:08:08,090 --> 00:08:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but a potential approach is to open 
something similar to a private school.</font>

127
00:08:11,810 --> 00:08:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it's at the church, 
people will have easy access.</font>

128
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This, in turn, increases people's trust 
in the church and attracts worshipers.</font>

129
00:08:18,870 --> 00:08:21,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It may be wishful thinking on my part,</font>

130
00:08:21,130 --> 00:08:24,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I believe it will also attract
more and more volunteers over time.</font>

131
00:08:24,470 --> 00:08:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-There's no way it'd go that well!</font>

132
00:08:26,670 --> 00:08:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, it'll be amazing!</font>

133
00:08:28,020 --> 00:08:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like those open-air classrooms!</font>

134
00:08:29,670 --> 00:08:32,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But what'll we do about study materials?</font>

135
00:08:32,670 --> 00:08:34,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what about our work in the almshouse?</font>

136
00:08:35,160 --> 00:08:37,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we organize the classes in shifts,</font>

137
00:08:37,350 --> 00:08:40,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they can be smaller,
 and study materials can be shared.</font>

138
00:08:42,250 --> 00:08:45,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We could split the almshouse 
children into three groups</font>

139
00:08:45,040 --> 00:08:49,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and have all of them take turns working 
and studying on different days.</font>

140
00:08:49,870 --> 00:08:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just learning basic reading, 
writing, and arithmetic</font>

141
00:08:52,540 --> 00:08:54,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will make you more valuable in town</font>

142
00:08:54,790 --> 00:08:56,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and broaden your job options.</font>

143
00:08:57,280 --> 00:09:01,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those with talent may even be able
 to pursue further education.</font>

144
00:09:02,020 --> 00:09:03,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You...</font>

145
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:06,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It'd be good to include 
a scholarship program.</i></font>

146
00:09:07,250 --> 00:09:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The royal family could invest in 
and subsidize gifted children.</i></font>

147
00:09:11,830 --> 00:09:14,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Nurturing talent will be highly beneficial</i></font>

148
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:16,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>for both the royal palace and the kingdom.</i></font>

149
00:09:17,020 --> 00:09:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With that decided, we should confirm 
the almshouse children's wishes.</font>

150
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:24,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold on a second! 
No one gave you permission to...</font>

151
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:26,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, Selio-kun.</font>

152
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on.</font>

153
00:09:28,580 --> 00:09:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm busy, so hurry up.</font>

154
00:09:32,390 --> 00:09:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You...</font>

155
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really hate you after all!</font>

156
00:09:39,530 --> 00:09:44,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard the bishop and the accountant 
are both currently away from the church.</font>

157
00:09:44,310 --> 00:09:45,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

158
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For some reason, they left despite being 
notified of the inspection dates.</font>

159
00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Luckily, that's made it easier
for me to gather documents.</font>

160
00:09:52,670 --> 00:09:55,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've urged them to return 
by the day after tomorrow.</font>

161
00:09:55,940 --> 00:09:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me what you make
 of the church so far.</font>

162
00:09:59,880 --> 00:10:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will include all the
 details in my report,</font>

163
00:10:02,670 --> 00:10:05,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there appear to be discrepancies 
between the titles and numbers</font>

164
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:08,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of nobles attending services
and their donations.</font>

165
00:10:08,910 --> 00:10:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Embezzlement, eh? Any idea 
where the money's going?</font>

166
00:10:12,460 --> 00:10:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still investigating, 
but at the very least, the almshouse,</font>

167
00:10:15,750 --> 00:10:18,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">monks-in-training, 
and their priest likely aren't involved.</font>

168
00:10:19,090 --> 00:10:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their priest...</font>

169
00:10:20,250 --> 00:10:22,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Priest Siegvold?</font>

170
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:23,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know him?</font>

171
00:10:23,770 --> 00:10:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's famous.</font>

172
00:10:25,630 --> 00:10:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not only is his family impressive,</font>

173
00:10:27,580 --> 00:10:30,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but his abundant magical energy
and looks are also top-notch.</font>

174
00:10:30,190 --> 00:10:32,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On the other hand, his intense 
faith makes it difficult</font>

175
00:10:32,770 --> 00:10:35,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">for the nobility to get
 their hands on him.</font>

176
00:10:35,780 --> 00:10:38,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His magical energy, you say?</font>

177
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:39,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

178
00:10:39,070 --> 00:10:43,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a precious resource required for
 both spellcasting and magical tools.</font>

179
00:10:43,410 --> 00:10:47,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's difficult to handle, demanding
special knowledge and skills.</font>

180
00:10:48,180 --> 00:10:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why children born 
with too much undergo training</font>

181
00:10:51,650 --> 00:10:55,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">at a church to learn how to 
reduce their magical energy.</font>

182
00:10:55,680 --> 00:10:57,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, Seichiro...</font>

183
00:10:57,700 --> 00:11:01,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's your resistance to 
magical energy and magicules?</font>

184
00:11:01,040 --> 00:11:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thankfully, I am slowly 
gaining some resistance.</font>

185
00:11:04,630 --> 00:11:06,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's good to hear.</font>

186
00:11:06,580 --> 00:11:12,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, you've already managed to grab
the reins of someone as famously difficult</font>

187
00:11:12,110 --> 00:11:14,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as Priest Siegvold.</font>

188
00:11:15,410 --> 00:11:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Grab the reins? You make him 
sound like a wild horse.</font>

189
00:11:20,540 --> 00:11:26,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People say he's a black beast. 
So rather than his reins...</font>

190
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:28,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps you're his chains?</font>

191
00:11:28,510 --> 00:11:29,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Excellency...</font>

192
00:11:30,330 --> 00:11:32,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not joking.</font>

193
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:36,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However you may feel about him, 
you have become his chains.</font>

194
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unlike Priest Siegvold's chains,
 you're perfectly tangible.</font>

195
00:11:43,320 --> 00:11:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention extremely fragile.</font>

196
00:11:47,670 --> 00:11:53,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I plan to help you as best I can, 
but it never hurts to be careful.</font>

197
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I am Aresh-sama's chains...</i></font>

198
00:11:58,740 --> 00:12:00,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's not just His Excellency.</i></font>

199
00:12:00,430 --> 00:12:04,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Everyone is starting to notice 
Aresh-sama's attachment to me.</i></font>

200
00:12:05,370 --> 00:12:07,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I appreciate your consideration.</font>

201
00:12:08,090 --> 00:12:12,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, I heard you want to open a private
 school for commoners in the church.</font>

202
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

203
00:12:15,630 --> 00:12:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

204
00:12:17,250 --> 00:12:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You truly are a talented individual.</font>

205
00:12:19,660 --> 00:12:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're even picking apart education now?</font>

206
00:12:22,230 --> 00:12:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

207
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:25,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was Her Holiness who originally
came up with the idea.</font>

208
00:12:25,940 --> 00:12:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I merely supported her proposal.</font>

209
00:12:28,900 --> 00:12:31,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm presently preparing an estimate
of the project's economic impact</font>

210
00:12:31,790 --> 00:12:33,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and will submit it to you in a few days.</font>

211
00:12:34,660 --> 00:12:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that is your area
 of expertise, after all.</font>

212
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:42,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's one thing I'd like to ask you.</font>

213
00:12:43,420 --> 00:12:44,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

214
00:12:48,110 --> 00:12:49,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seichiro.</font>

215
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it that you want 
to do to this kingdom?</font>

216
00:12:56,690 --> 00:12:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

217
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:02,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have no attachment to this kingdom.</i></font>

218
00:13:02,010 --> 00:13:05,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just want to make this place 
easier for me to do my job.</i></font>

219
00:13:06,430 --> 00:13:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sorcery department 
is sorely lacking in personnel.</font>

220
00:13:09,110 --> 00:13:12,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is causing delays in 
miasma countermeasures</font>

221
00:13:12,100 --> 00:13:13,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the return spell's development.</font>

222
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:18,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You truly are...</font>

223
00:13:19,640 --> 00:13:24,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Overlooking talented people
means massive losses for the land.</font>

224
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a waste not to be 
cost-effective in doing business.</font>

225
00:13:30,140 --> 00:13:33,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're absolutely right.</font>

226
00:13:33,720 --> 00:13:35,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, what a pity.</font>

227
00:13:35,840 --> 00:13:38,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a pity, Seichiro.</font>

228
00:13:39,280 --> 00:13:40,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Truly...</font>

229
00:13:40,800 --> 00:13:47,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it weren't for that black beast, 
I would have taken such good care of you.</font>

230
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:51,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I appreciate the thought.</font>

231
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here, Seiichirou?</font>

232
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:01,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-sama...</font>

233
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:04,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I swear...</font>

234
00:14:04,750 --> 00:14:07,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many times must I tell you
 before you understand?</font>

235
00:14:07,130 --> 00:14:10,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't the purification expedition
 the day after tomorrow?</font>

236
00:14:10,940 --> 00:14:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shouldn't you be preparing?</font>

237
00:14:12,570 --> 00:14:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milan took care of that ages ago.</font>

238
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:17,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to prepare more than I do.</font>

239
00:14:17,950 --> 00:14:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me?</font>

240
00:14:19,470 --> 00:14:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't be by your side for some time.</font>

241
00:14:21,990 --> 00:14:24,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll need a thoroughly cast barrier.</font>

242
00:14:24,520 --> 00:14:26,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, um...</font>

243
00:14:26,980 --> 00:14:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have tomorrow off in 
advance of the expedition.</font>

244
00:14:30,160 --> 00:14:32,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have plenty of time.</font>

245
00:14:32,060 --> 00:14:34,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have work tomorrow, 
so let's keep it brief...</font>

246
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be ridiculous.</font>

247
00:14:37,200 --> 00:14:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way I'd squander 
an opportunity to touch you.</font>

248
00:14:43,010 --> 00:14:45,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd do well to remember that.</font>

249
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:51,740
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}DAY OF THE EXPEDITION DEPARTURE</font>

250
00:14:58,200 --> 00:15:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm off, Seiichirou.</font>

251
00:15:05,530 --> 00:15:08,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care of Seiichirou
 for me while I'm gone.</font>

252
00:15:08,250 --> 00:15:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can leave him to us.</font>

253
00:15:10,250 --> 00:15:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Check on him regularly to make 
sure he's not sacrificing sleep.</font>

254
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:16,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He tends to bury himself
in work when I'm not around.</font>

255
00:15:16,380 --> 00:15:17,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

256
00:15:18,460 --> 00:15:20,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give him a talking-to if 
he doesn't finish his lunch.</font>

257
00:15:20,990 --> 00:15:22,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Master.</font>

258
00:15:23,050 --> 00:15:25,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure he actually rests on days off.</font>

259
00:15:25,510 --> 00:15:28,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And have him tell you where he's 
going whenever he goes out.</font>

260
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:30,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milord.</font>

261
00:15:30,260 --> 00:15:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he lies and goes to work
 on his day off...</font>

262
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:34,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Young Master!</font>

263
00:15:35,010 --> 00:15:39,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand your worries, 
but please leave everything to us.</font>

264
00:15:41,260 --> 00:15:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never thought you would care 
this deeply for another.</font>

265
00:15:49,110 --> 00:15:52,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though work comes 
first for Kondu-sama,</font>

266
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure he will be more eager
 than anyone for your safe return.</font>

267
00:15:56,330 --> 00:15:58,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think so, too.</font>

268
00:15:58,490 --> 00:16:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll be there to happily 
welcome you home.</font>

269
00:16:06,940 --> 00:16:08,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He will, will he?</font>

270
00:16:10,650 --> 00:16:12,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope that's the case...</font>

271
00:16:13,070 --> 00:16:14,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-sama!</font>

272
00:16:18,160 --> 00:16:19,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seiichirou.</font>

273
00:16:21,180 --> 00:16:23,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you about to depart?</font>

274
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:25,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could have stayed in bed.</font>

275
00:16:25,370 --> 00:16:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't have.</font>

276
00:16:27,060 --> 00:16:31,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're leaving on an important mission.
The least I can do is see you off.</font>

277
00:16:37,340 --> 00:16:38,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-sama...</font>

278
00:16:38,950 --> 00:16:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

279
00:16:40,810 --> 00:16:42,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall await your safe return.</font>

280
00:16:43,600 --> 00:16:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care not to get injured.</font>

281
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can use recovery magic if I do.</font>

282
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:54,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, that was an absurd request
to ask of a knight like you...</font>

283
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:02,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

284
00:17:02,760 --> 00:17:04,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one can see us behind my cloak.</font>

285
00:17:05,680 --> 00:17:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not the problem here!</font>

286
00:17:10,870 --> 00:17:14,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today, I'll meet the bishop and 
accountant, who have finally returned.</i></font>

287
00:17:16,170 --> 00:17:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's finally time for you
 to pay your dues!</font>

288
00:17:19,060 --> 00:17:22,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one asking for overdue payment.</font>

289
00:17:22,090 --> 00:17:24,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're always so picky about everything.</font>

290
00:17:24,430 --> 00:17:27,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it, Shiraishi...</font>

291
00:17:27,420 --> 00:17:30,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her Holiness said she won't be
 at the church for a while.</font>

292
00:17:30,270 --> 00:17:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She asked me to say hello.</font>

293
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:33,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, you...</font>

294
00:17:33,760 --> 00:17:36,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if you're a friend 
of the holy maiden,</font>

295
00:17:36,060 --> 00:17:39,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll never accept someone
 who just tagged along with her</font>

296
00:17:39,840 --> 00:17:41,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and acts so high and mighty all the time!</font>

297
00:17:42,330 --> 00:17:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ignorance is a road to ruin.</font>

298
00:17:42,740 --> 00:17:44,160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}HEH...</font>

299
00:17:44,750 --> 00:17:47,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once the private school opens, 
do attend, Selio-san.</font>

300
00:17:47,410 --> 00:17:50,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! Did you just make fun of me?!</font>

301
00:17:52,440 --> 00:17:56,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aresh-sama will return in seven 
days at the very latest.</i></font>

302
00:17:56,360 --> 00:17:58,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I should do all I can in that time.</i></font>

303
00:18:00,360 --> 00:18:05,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're the rumored otherworlder?
 I've heard about you.</font>

304
00:18:06,040 --> 00:18:10,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's taking a blatantly hostile attitude
with a representative from the palace.</i></font>

305
00:18:10,500 --> 00:18:13,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hard not to see the defiance in his heart.</i></font>

306
00:18:14,140 --> 00:18:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Mateus, the royal capital's bishop.</font>

307
00:18:17,560 --> 00:18:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Cipriano, the one in 
charge of the church's finances.</font>

308
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:23,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you.</font>

309
00:18:23,590 --> 00:18:25,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Likewise.</font>

310
00:18:25,030 --> 00:18:29,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm very sorry the income 
and expenses report is late.</font>

311
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In truth, we were very busy supporting 
the summoning of the holy maiden and...</font>

312
00:18:34,820 --> 00:18:37,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This man seems friendly.</i></font>

313
00:18:37,080 --> 00:18:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He lost the report and, because he was 
busy, couldn't meet the deadline.</i></font>

314
00:18:43,250 --> 00:18:44,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

315
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, the deadline is the deadline.</font>

316
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:49,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now you've suddenly asked us
to care for the holy maiden, too.</font>

317
00:18:49,910 --> 00:18:53,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe your side is also to blame
 for our hectic schedule.</font>

318
00:18:53,530 --> 00:18:55,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Your Excellency.</font>

319
00:18:55,230 --> 00:18:59,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We already knew Her Holiness
would be coming to the church.</font>

320
00:18:59,510 --> 00:19:02,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The delay was entirely my fault.</font>

321
00:19:02,940 --> 00:19:06,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, are you still in the process
of preparing the report?</font>

322
00:19:06,540 --> 00:19:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I'm very sorry.</font>

323
00:19:09,560 --> 00:19:13,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, I will continue 
commuting here for a while longer.</font>

324
00:19:13,470 --> 00:19:16,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We are planning to open a cram school 
in the name of the holy maiden,</font>

325
00:19:16,620 --> 00:19:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so this works out perfectly.</font>

326
00:19:18,330 --> 00:19:19,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cram school?</font>

327
00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:20,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

328
00:19:20,810 --> 00:19:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It will be a place to teach 
simple subjects to children</font>

329
00:19:24,100 --> 00:19:26,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who cannot normally attend school 
due to their circumstances.</font>

330
00:19:26,890 --> 00:19:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a wonderful idea!</font>

331
00:19:28,220 --> 00:19:30,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As expected of the holy maiden 
and Abran's disciple!</font>

332
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In this fashion, we hope to increase 
donations and elevate the church.</font>

333
00:19:37,930 --> 00:19:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A favorable reaction.</i></font>

334
00:19:39,500 --> 00:19:41,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>People who are easy to read
 are easy to handle.</i></font>

335
00:19:43,650 --> 00:19:46,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew there was no mistake 
when Abran chose you!</font>

336
00:19:46,960 --> 00:19:49,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please allow me to assist you, Disciple!</font>

337
00:19:49,750 --> 00:19:52,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>People like him are convenient 
at times like these.</i></font>

338
00:19:54,210 --> 00:19:56,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And so the days passed.</i></font>

339
00:19:59,260 --> 00:20:01,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In the afternoon of the seventh
day since the expedition,</i></font>

340
00:20:01,760 --> 00:20:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the church suddenly grew lively.</i></font>

341
00:20:05,800 --> 00:20:09,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her Holiness has successfully 
purified the miasma!</font>

342
00:20:13,670 --> 00:20:14,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

343
00:20:14,840 --> 00:20:17,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-sama hasn't returned yet?</font>

344
00:20:17,700 --> 00:20:18,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

345
00:20:18,900 --> 00:20:22,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems the purification was 
completed without incident,</font>

346
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:25,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but a herd of ferocious beasts was 
spotted in the mountains nearby,</font>

347
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so instead of returning home, 
he immediately went to subjugate them.</font>

348
00:20:32,830 --> 00:20:35,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see...</font>

349
00:20:36,120 --> 00:20:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondu-sama.</font>

350
00:20:38,560 --> 00:20:42,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I received this from a returning
 member of the expedition.</font>

351
00:20:42,740 --> 00:20:44,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's from Aresh-sama.</font>

352
00:20:52,310 --> 00:20:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Dear Seiichirou."</font>

353
00:20:54,430 --> 00:20:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"I'm sure you've already heard,</i></font>

354
00:20:57,040 --> 00:21:00,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I have decided to remain in the 
area to subjugate magic beasts..."</i></font>

355
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:05,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Please take good care of 
yourself while I am away.</i></font>

356
00:21:05,730 --> 00:21:08,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't work too hard, 
and get plenty of rest.</i></font>

357
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:11,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even in letters...</i></font>

358
00:21:13,980 --> 00:21:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But thank goodness.</i></font>

359
00:21:17,040 --> 00:21:18,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It wasn't bad news.</i></font>

360
00:21:23,890 --> 00:21:27,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I hope you fall to slumber with my soul.</i></font>

361
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:32,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His soul? What an odd thing to say...</i></font>

362
00:21:33,130 --> 00:21:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me, Milan-san.</font>

363
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:35,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

364
00:21:35,900 --> 00:21:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know what this sentence means?</font>

365
00:21:40,320 --> 00:21:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my!</font>

366
00:21:42,180 --> 00:21:45,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milord is so passionate!</font>

367
00:21:45,550 --> 00:21:46,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

368
00:21:46,540 --> 00:21:51,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For a knight, his soul is an 
expression for his feelings.</font>

369
00:21:51,470 --> 00:21:53,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words...</font>

370
00:21:54,310 --> 00:21:58,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I hope you fall asleep 
thinking of me by your side."</font>

371
00:23:35,090 --> 00:23:40,170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}EPISODE 10
I INVESTIGATED</font>

